text: Papassara Techapaibul () (born November 24, 1969 in Thailand) is Miss Thailand World 1988. She competed in Miss World 1988 in the United Kingdom. Currently, she work as a drama television actress and director. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Miss World 1988 delegates Category:Thai actresses Category:Thai beauty pageant winners
